</description><media:thumbnail url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/9c153156-0466-11ec-bcf1-005056a97e36/w:1024/p:16x9/Capture-747.PNG"/><enclosure url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/9c153156-0466-11ec-bcf1-005056a97e36/w:1024/p:16x9/Capture-747.PNG" type="image/png" length="0"/><guid isPermaLink="false">019927c0-0463-11ec-8ca7-005056bf762b</guid><pubDate>Mon, 23 Aug 2021 22:39:34 GMT</pubDate><source url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/9c153156-0466-11ec-bcf1-005056a97e36/w:1024/p:16x9/Capture-747.PNG">© 網絡圖片</source><dc:creator>弗林</dc:creator></item><item><category>亞洲</category><title>印度和菲律賓在南海舉行海上合作演習</title><link>https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2/20210823-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%92%8C%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E6%B5%B7%E4%B8%8A%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E6%BC%94%E7%BF%92</link><description>
